caption.p: Relative mRNA levels of ERβ (A), Bcl‐2 (B), Bax (C), and VEGFR (D) using quantitative PCR in ovary tissue of female mice. Data are presented as mean ± SEM, n = 8. Results are normalized to β‐actin. Control: diet without MOL, 4% MOL: diet supplemented with 4% MOL, and 8% MOL: diet supplemented with 8% MOL
